Package fitness_classes

Class FitnessClass

java.lang.Object
fitness_classes.FitnessClass
public class FitnessClass extends Object
This class defines all the characteristics of a fitness class. This includes:
  • ArrayList Members In Class
  • ArrayList Guest Members In Class
  • Time Time
  • String Class Name
  • String Instructor Name
  • Location Gym Location
Author:
Hasnain Ali, Carolette Saguil

      Parameters:
      time - Time of fitness class.
      className - Name of fitness class.
      instructorName - Name of instructor for fitness class.

    • checkIfMemberExpired

      public boolean checkIfMemberExpired(Member member)

      **Please note, if membership expires today, the membership is considered expired**

      Returns:

    • checkIn

      public boolean checkIn(Member member)
      Checks in member to fitness class. Adds member to members in class array list. Fails if: member's membership is expired or if they are already in class.
      Parameters:
      member - Member to check in.
      Returns:
      true if member is added to members in class array list, false otherwise.
